(1, 'Kayaka’s philosophy and values in imparting knowledge has its own identity. It’s curriculum is value based, as required by industry requirement and customer needs.Thus, the students become a part of its group working at the same frequency creating a stimulating learning ambience. An advantage of learning and getting training in Kayaka has its own merits.', 3, 'YES', '', '0000-00-00', '0000-00-00', 'WIDGET'),
(2, 'JOB FAIR 2015 is organized on July 25th, 2015. Top Notch companies are participating in the Job Fair. An open JOB FAIR which requires Accountant, Team Leaders, Team Managers, Business Development Executives, Process Associates, HR Executives, Technical Support and much more. This event is a unique opportunity for experienced professionals and fresher’s to get interviewed on the spot by top companies.', 0, 'YES', '', '0000-00-00', '0000-00-00', 'WIDGET'),
(3, 'Our innovative training methodology is a result of years of research by educationists & human resource professionals. KAYAKA has been recognized by a number of Government and Non - Government organizations in and around Bangalore. Thus, the students become a part of its group working at the same frequency creating a stimulating learning ambience. An advantage of learning and getting training in Kayaka has its own merits.', 1, 'YES', '', '2014-07-01', '9999-12-30', 'WIDGET'),
(4, 'Plan and Prepare for Bank Exams for RBI/LIC/GIC/SSC/RRB/Central & State Gov. Get expert guidance with our well equpied classroom sessions delivered by experienced trainers. Our classroom sessions for bank exams focus on conceptual clarity and ample practice, thereby making you to adept across all sections of your target exam. It\\\'s a course which covers all the subjects in the classroom teaching hours and with more number of hours of testing.', 2, 'YES', '', '2014-07-01', '9999-12-30', 'WIDGET');
