part strength and efficiency.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;&quot;&gt;Read more....&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;</column-text><item-margin>42</item-margin></Column><Column><size>element1-3</size><header>Announcements</header><column-text>[news-announcement group=&quot;widget&quot;]\r\n\r\n</column-text><item-margin>45</item-margin></Column><About-Us><size>element1-1</size><header>About Us</header><image>3460</image><content>KAYAKA was established in the year 1999 which has successfully undergone training for more over 3 lacs learners from all sectors till date. Later in 2007 it has been incorporated as KAYAKA COMPUTER EDUCATION (P) LTD.  Kayaka, not only limits its services in the urban areas but also provides more effective service in and around Karnataka in the field of Computerized Accounts through Tally.ERP 9, Software, Hardware and Networking, CAD, Mobile Technology, Spoken English, Data Management and Analysis using Advanced Excel, Soft Skills Training &amp; Banking Coaching classes to fulfil the learners with Computer literacy to avail better employment.                   \r\nOur innovative training methodology is a result of years of research by educationalists and human resource professionals. We welcome Students, Employees, Individuals, Businessmen and people from all walks of life to groom their career for success. </content><button-text>Read more......</button-text><button-link>#</button-link><enable-pdf>No</enable-pdf><item-margin>40</item-margin></About-Us><Column><size>element1-3</size><header>Our Mission</header><column-text>&lt;div class=\'animatedParent\'&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;row omsr animated pulse delay-300&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;twelve columns stunning-text-item-class stunning-text-item-class-1 oms&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;stunning-text-wrapper gdl-border-x top&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;stunning-text-inner-wrapper gdl-border-x bottom&quot;&gt;&lt;d