(3341, 1, '2013-03-07 08:23:35', '2013-03-07 08:23:35', '[vc_row el_id="abtid" el_class="abtcls"][vc_column css_animation="none" width="1/2" css=".vc_custom_1522072227874{background-image: url(http://localhost/kayaka/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/slide1.jpg?id=3460) !important;background-position: center !important;background-repeat: no-repeat !important;background-size: cover !important;}" el_id="imgid1" el_class="imgcls1"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2" el_id="kayid" el_class="kaycls"][vc_column_text css_animation="none" el_class="abcls" el_id="abid"]KAYAKA was established in the year 1999 which has successfully undergone training for more over 3 lacs learners from all sectors till date. Later in 2007 it has been incorporated as KAYAKA COMPUTER EDUCATION (P) LTD. Kayaka, not only limits its services in the urban areas but also provides more effective service in and around Karnataka in the field of Computerized Accounts through Tally.ERP 9, Software, Hardware and Networking, CAD, Mobile Technology, Spoken English, Data Management and Analysis using Advanced Excel, Soft Skills Training &amp; Banking Coaching classes to fulfil the learners with Computer literacy to avail better employment. [/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row el_id="rid1" el_class="rcls1"][vc_column width="1/2" el_id="kayid2" el_class="kaycls2"][vc_column_text css_animation="none" el_id="abtid2" el_class="abtcls2"]Our innovative training methodology is a result of years of research by educationalists and human resource professionals. We welcome Students, Employees, Individuals, Businessmen and people from all walks of life to groom their career for success. Our training course inspires and encourages them to reach for their goals. The various courses which are offered through Certificate courses are constantly updated according to the current trend in the IT industry. Training is conducted in comfortable and spacious labs equipped with computers which are constantly updated with the latest technology.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column css_animation="none" width="1/2" css=".vc_custom_1522071922160{background-image: url(http://localhost/kayaka/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/corporate_training9-1-639x359.jpg?id=3541) !important;background-position: center !important;background-repeat: no-repeat !important;background-size: cover !important;}" el_id="imgid2" el_class="imgcls2"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row el_id="rid2" el_class="rc2"][vc_column css_animation="none" width="1/2" css=".vc_custom_1522071885959{background-image: url(http://localhost/kayaka/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/3-1.jpg?id=3546) !important;background-position: center !important;background-repeat: no-repeat !important;background-size: cover !important;}" el_id="imgid3" el_class="imgcls3"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2" el_id="kayid3" el_class="kaycls3"][vc_column_text css_animation="none" el_id="abtid3" el_class="abtcls3"]We are Tally Authorized training provider known as Tally Institute of Learning TIL and also Master Tally Assessment partner in Karnataka region. Certification in Tally.ERP9 gives a competitive edge with Tally software training certifications from Tally Academy. Globally recognized, Tally certifications demonstrate that you have honed your skills through rigorous study and direct experience in your area of expertise. The key features of our TIL are scientifically designed teaching methodology, industry relevant curriculum/ courseware, training delivery by Tally certified faculty, with effective theory to practical sessions, online assessments, verifiable certification and 100% placement assistance.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row el_id="rid3" el_class="rcl3"][vc_column width="1/2" el_id="kayid4" el_class="kaycls4"][vc_column_text el_id="abtid4" el_class="abtcls4"]Tally powers more than 90% of business houses in India. This propels demand for Tally trained professionals. With Tally being used in more than 100 countries, students gain access to global placement opportunities. Concentrating more over Practical’s rather than Theory which clarifies concepts and prepares a learner to handle real world scenarios with confidence. Faculties are highly experienced, well equipped, and competent and trained by Tally. Regular practice sessions and online assessments help a learner to identify the areas of improvement and work towards it for improvement. Owning a Verifiable certificate from Tally Institute of Learning which is a unique certificate ID and the same can be used to access the certificate online any time.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2" css=".vc_custom_1522073350205{background-image: url(http://localhost/kayaka/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/8-1.jpg?id=3550) !important;background-position: center !important;background-repeat: no-repeat !important;background-size: cover !important;}" el_id="imgid4" el_class="imgcls4"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text]\r\n<div class="applybs">\r\n<div class="row">\r\n<div class="col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-xs-12">\r\n<div class="ed_transprentbg ed_toppadder80 ed_bottompadder40">\r\n<div class="container">\r\n<div class="row">\r\n<div class="col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-sm-12 col-xs-12">\r\n<div class="ed_heading_top ed_bottompadder50">\r\n<h3 class="text-center">ourTrainers</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="ed_team_wrapper">\r\n<div class="col-lg-3 col-md-3 col-sm-4 col-xs-12 animatedParent">\r\n<div class="ed_team_member animated bounceInDown">\r\n<div class="ed_team_member_img">\r\n\r\n<img class="img-responsive" src="http://localhost/kayaka/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/dummy2-490x560.png" alt="M.Durgarani" />\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="ed_team_member_description">\r\n<h4><a href="#">M.Durgarani</a></h4>\r\n<h5>English Teacher</h5>\r\nShe charms of pleasure of the moment, so blinded by desire foresee.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="col-lg-3 col-md-3 col-sm-4 col-xs-12 animatedParent">\r\n<div class="ed_team_member animated bounceInUp">\r\