echnology.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column css_animation="none" width="1/2" css=".vc_custom_1522071922160{background-image: url(http://localhost/kayaka/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/corporate_training9-1-639x359.jpg?id=3541) !important;background-position: center !important;background-repeat: no-repeat !important;background-size: cover !important;}" el_id="imgid2" el_class="imgcls2"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row el_id="rid2" el_class="rc2"][vc_column css_animation="none" width="1/2" css=".vc_custom_1522071885959{background-image: url(http://localhost/kayaka/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/3-1.jpg?id=3546) !important;background-position: center !important;background-repeat: no-repeat !important;background-size: cover !important;}" el_id="imgid3" el_class="imgcls3"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2" el_id="kayid3" el_class="kaycls3"][vc_column_text css_animation="none" el_id="abtid3" el_class="abtcls3"]We are Tally Authorized training provider known as Tally Institute of Learning TIL and also Master Tally Assessment partner in Karnataka region. Certification in Tally.ERP9 gives a competitive edge with Tally software training certifications from Tally Academy. Globally recognized, Tally certifications demonstrate that you have honed your skills through rigorous study and direct experience in your area of expertise. The key features of our TIL are scientifically designed teaching methodology, industry relevant curriculum/ courseware, training delivery by Tally certified faculty, with effective theory to practical sessions, online assessments, verifiable certification and 100% placement assistance.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row el_id="rid4" el_class="rcls4"][vc_column width="1/2" el_id="kayid4" el_class="kaycls4"][vc_column_text el_id="abtid4" el_class="abtcls4"]Tally powers more than 90% of business houses in India. This propels demand for Tally trained professionals. With Tally being used in more than 100 countries, students gain access to global placement opportunities. Concentrating more over Practical’s rather than Theory which clarifies concepts and prepares a learner to handle real world scenarios with confidence. Faculties are highly experienced, well equipped, and competent and trained by Tally. Regular practice sessions and online assessments help a learner to identify the areas of improvement and work towards it for improvement. Owning a Verifiable certificate from Tally Institute of Learning which is a unique certificate ID and the same can be used to access the certificate online any time.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2" css=".vc_custom_1522073350205{background-image: url(http://localhost/kayaka/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/8-1.jpg?id=3550) !important;background-position: center !important;background-repeat: no-repeat !important;background-size: cover !important;}" el_id="imgid4" el_class="imgcls4"][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'About Us', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '3341-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-03-26 14:10:52', '2018-03-26 14:10:52', '', 3341, 'http://localhost/kayaka/index.php/2018/03/26/3341-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
