(3597, 1, '2018-03-28 13:45:32', '2018-03-28 13:45:32', '[vc_row el_id="course2id" el_class="corse2cls"][vc_column css_animation="fadeInLeft" width="2/3" css=".vc_custom_1522242815793{background-image: url(http://localhost/kayaka/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/spokenenglish.jpg?id=3587) !important;background-position: center !important;background-repeat: no-repeat !important;background-size: cover !important;}" el_id="c1id" el_class="c1cls"][/vc_column][vc_column css_animation="fadeInRight" width="1/3" el_id="newsid" el_class="newscls"][vc_column_text][news-announcement group="widget"][/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css=".vc_custom_1522240567617{background-color: #f4f4f4 !important;}"][vc_column][vc_tta_tabs active_section="1" css_animation="fadeIn" el_id="contid" el_class="contclass"][vc_tta_section i_position="right" i_icon_fontawesome="fa fa-desktop" add_icon="true" title="Course Info" tab_id="1522240189758-b560af7d-ab63"][vc_column_text css_animation="none"]\r\n<h3 style="text-align: center;"><strong>SPOKEN ENGLISH</strong></h3>\r\nCommunication is a general phenomenon. It occurs in the universe, wherever life occurs. We cannot survive without communicating. In that, English language is the topmost language globally used for communication. Grammar is the most essential for English language. We use grammar whenever we speak or write. Grammar is the system by which a language works.[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section i_position="right" i_icon_fontawesome="fa fa-info-circle" add_icon="true" title="Course Details" tab_id="1522240189931-9ce6ea30-27dc"][vc_column_text css_animation="none"]\r\n<h3 style="text-align: center;"><strong>COURSE DETAILS</strong></h3>\r\nTo enhance learners, we provide\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Basic English (Listening, Reading, Writing, Pronunciation, Word Building, Vocabulary).</li>\r\n 	<li>Structural English (Parts of Speech, Tenses, Direct &amp; Indirect Speech, Letter Writing, Paragraph Writing).</li>\r\n 	<li>Communicative English (Seeking Permission, Asking for Advice, Environmental Conversation, Drafting Bio-Data, Resume).</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section i_position="right" i_icon_fontawesome="fa fa-trophy" add_icon="true" title="Merits" tab_id="1522240190131-957dd34e-410f"][vc_column_text css_animation="none"]\r\n<h3 style="text-align: center;"><strong>MERITS</strong></h3>\r\nNow days, to become proficiency. English is very essential. This course also helps to empower their Business language. On completion of this course students are enable to enrich their vocabulary, pronunciation, word building, enhance their knowledge in usage of grammar by understanding Parts of speech, Articles and Tenses etc., and also communicative skill to master both Verbal and Non-Verbal communication. They will be able to get experience of speaking real English by involving in various group discussions, pick-and-speak, mock interviews, etc.,[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section i_position="right" i_icon_fontawesome="fa fa-hand-peace-o" add_icon="true" title="Highlights" tab_id="1522240190236-268daf5b-3ad7"][vc_column_text css_animation="none"]\r\n<h3 style="text-align: center;"><strong>HIGHLIGHTS</strong></h3>\r\nWe provide many advanced courses in our institution where Spoken English is also one among the leading course. We provide Spoken English course to promote employment opportunities. We groom their confidence, personality by training on various skills such as Interview skill, Communicative skill and also interpersonal skill. On successful completion of the course, students are capable of speaking fluent English. We have trained thousands of candidates from various categories.[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][/vc_tta_tabs][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'DATA MANAGEMENT AND ANALYSIS USING ADVANCED EXCEL', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '3595-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-03-28 13:45:32', '2018-03-28 13:45:32', '', 3595, 'http://localhost/kayaka/index.