(3615, 1, '2018-03-28 14:36:36', '2018-03-28 14:36:36', '[vc_row el_id="course4id" el_class="corse4cls"][vc_column css_animation="fadeInLeft" width="2/3" css=".vc_custom_1522247744066{background-image: url(http://localhost/kayaka/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/New-Project-1-2.jpg?id=3614) !important;background-position: center !important;background-repeat: no-repeat !important;background-size: cover !important;}" el_id="c1id" el_class="c1cls"][/vc_column][vc_column css_animation="fadeInRight" width="1/3" el_id="newsid" el_class="newscls"][vc_column_text][news-announcement group="widget"][/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css=".vc_custom_1522240567617{background-color: #f4f4f4 !important;}"][vc_column][vc_tta_tabs active_section="1" css_animation="fadeIn" el_id="contid" el_class="contclass"][vc_tta_section i_position="right" i_icon_fontawesome="fa fa-desktop" add_icon="true" title="Course Info" tab_id="1522240189758-b560af7d-ab63"][vc_column_text css_animation="none"]\r\n<h3 style="text-align: center;"><strong>DATA MANAGEMENT AND ANALYSIS USING ADVANCED EXCEL\r\n</strong></h3>\r\nWe believe in effective training and tangible results which is why our Advanced Excel Course concentrates on Excel features and techniques that you will be able to apply every day in order to make your spreadsheets more reliable, efficient, automatic and to give them maximum outcomes. Each of the areas our syllabus addresses is intended to equip you with knowledge and techniques that you will be able to use over and over again to not only make your own spreadsheets better, but also to enable you to help your colleagues and solve their Excel problems.[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section i_position="right" i_icon_fontawesome="fa fa-info-circle" add_icon="true" title="Course Details" tab_id="1522240189931-9ce6ea30-27dc"][vc_column_text css_animation="none"]\r\n<h3 style="text-align: center;"><strong>COURSE DETAILS</strong></h3>\r\nThe training exposure will be practical with the contents of\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Add-in and automation functions</li>\r\n 	<li>Summarizing, consolidating, and outlining data</li>\r\n 	<li>Importing &amp; exporting data from other sources</li>\r\n 	<li>Creating &amp; working with what-if analysis tools</li>\r\n 	<li>Working with Illustration</li>\r\n 	<li>Automation and programmability</li>\r\n 	<li>Workbook management</li>\r\n 	<li>Working with Text, Logical, Date &amp; Time, Financial, Lookup Formula</li>\r\n 	<li>Filtering, sorting, and conditionally formatting data</li>\r\n 	<li>Validating data</li>\r\n 	<li>Using &amp; Customizing Pivot Table &amp; Pivot Chart</li>\r\n 	<li>Excel and the Web</li>\r\n 	<li>Working in a different language</li>\r\n 	<li>Collaboration of Excel Sheet</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section i_position="right" i_icon_fontawesome="fa fa-trophy" add_icon="true" title="Merits" tab_id="1522240190131-957dd34e-410f"][vc_column_text css_animation="none"]\r\n<h3 style="text-align: center;"><strong>MERITS</strong></h3>\r\nMaster Shortcuts, functions and formulas that save time and increases productivity. Reduces workload at every interval of time by automating repetitive tasks by using macros. Learning how to use Advance Excel to its maximum potential will add a weight age, improves your skills and will open up more opportunities for employment.\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section i_position="right" i_icon_fontawesome="fa fa-hand-peace-o" add_icon="true" title="Highlights" tab_id="1522240190236-268daf5b-3ad7"][vc_column_text css_animation="none"]\r\n<h3 style="text-align: center;"><strong>HIGHLIGHTS</strong></h3>\r\nThe most important highlight is we have primed the deliverable with different scenario of an organization. The book will equip you with excellent Excel skills, good enough to learn quickly. Instruction is logically structured into sessions and lessons.\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][/vc_tta_tabs][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'SOFTWARE TRAINING', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '3604-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-03-28 14:36:36', '2018-03-28 14:36:36', '', 3604, 'http://localhost/kayaka/index.php/2018/03/28/3604-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
