(3626, 1, '2018-03-28 14:53:06', '2018-03-28 14:53:06', '[vc_row el_id="course4id" el_class="corse4cls"][vc_column css_animation="fadeInLeft" width="2/3" css=".vc_custom_1522248352217{background-image: url(http://localhost/kayaka/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/softskills-2.jpg?id=3622) !important;background-position: center !important;background-repeat: no-repeat !important;background-size: cover !important;}" el_id="c1id" el_class="c1cls"][/vc_column][vc_column css_animation="fadeInRight" width="1/3" el_id="newsid" el_class="newscls"][vc_column_text][news-announcement group="widget"][/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css=".vc_custom_1522240567617{background-color: #f4f4f4 !important;}"][vc_column][vc_tta_tabs active_section="1" css_animation="fadeIn" el_id="contid" el_class="contclass"][vc_tta_section i_position="right" i_icon_fontawesome="fa fa-desktop" add_icon="true" title="Course Info" tab_id="1522240189758-b560af7d-ab63"][vc_column_text css_animation="none"]\r\n<h3 style="text-align: center;"><strong>SOFT SKILLS TRAINING\r\n</strong></h3>\r\nSoft Skills is an Holistic Wellness Program where we boost one\'s confidence, improving communicative ability, widening one\'s scope of knowledge, learning fine etiquettes, adding style and grace to the way one looks, talks and overall shining oneself with positivity, liveliness and peace. Each individual has a distinct personality that can be developed, polished and refined.\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section i_position="right" i_icon_fontawesome="fa fa-info-circle" add_icon="true" title="Course Details" tab_id="1522240189931-9ce6ea30-27dc"][vc_column_text css_animation="none"]\r\n<h3 style="text-align: center;"><strong>COURSE DETAILS</strong></h3>\r\nTo groom the personality of individual we train on various topics such as\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Self Esteem</li>\r\n 	<li>Team Building</li>\r\n 	<li>Problem Solving</li>\r\n 	<li>Time Management</li>\r\n 	<li>Problem Solving</li>\r\n 	<li>Interpersonal Skills</li>\r\n 	<li>Presentation Skills</li>\r\n 	<li>Stress Management</li>\r\n 	<li>Marketing Skills</li>\r\n 	<li>Interview Skills</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section i_position="right" i_icon_fontawesome="fa fa-trophy" add_icon="true" title="Merits" tab_id="1522240190131-957dd34e-410f"][vc_column_text css_animation="none"]\r\n<h3 style="text-align: center;"><strong>MERITS</strong></h3>\r\nSoft Skill is necessary for the whole sole development of body, mind and character which are the prime building blocks for success. This training eradicates one\'s Stage fear, Pessimistic mentality, etc., and builds Confidence, Positive attitude and also enhances one\'s presentation skills.\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section i_position="right" i_icon_fontawesome="fa fa-hand-peace-o" add_icon="true" title="Highlights" tab_id="1522240190236-268daf5b-3ad7"][vc_column_text css_animation="none"]\r\n<h3 style="text-align: center;"><strong>HIGHLIGHTS</strong></h3>\r\nWe provide Soft Skills for the students those who have graduated from Spoken English. This training shines one\'s language. This has become a meritorious course in KAYAKA where we conducted many sessions on Soft Skills. To give some more added values to standardize their language, learners switch on to this unique training which is oriented on Personality development.\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][/vc_tta_tabs][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'HARDWARE & NETWORKING', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '3624-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-03-28 14:53:06', '2018-03-28 14:53:06', '', 3624, 'http://localhost/kayaka/index.php/2018/03/28/3624-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
