rong>CMOS Section</strong></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>VGA Section</strong></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Troubleshooting</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section i_position="right" i_icon_fontawesome="fa fa-trophy" add_icon="true" title="Merits" tab_id="1522240190131-957dd34e-410f"][vc_column_text css_animation="none"]\r\n<h3 style="text-align: center;"><strong>MERITS</strong></h3>\r\nThe teaching staffs have a background of electronics graduation with more than 10 years of chip level repairs experience backup. So here students not only understand the basic electronics, basic working phenomena of motherboards which is an essential for this profession to learn the real practical experience of repair.\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section i_position="right" i_icon_fontawesome="fa fa-hand-peace-o" add_icon="true" title="Highlights" tab_id="1522240190236-268daf5b-3ad7"][vc_column_text css_animation="none"]\r\n<h3 style="text-align: center;"><strong>HIGHLIGHTS</strong></h3>\r\nWe also have an infrastructure in such a way that each student will have their own individual testing equipments and tools to concentrate and learn in proper way during course period. We organized ourselves in such a way that we concentrate on each student by understanding his/her capability and teach according to it. So this course is not only suitable to the fresh students but also to the people who are already in the field and struggling to understand the systematic concept of repair. We assure that we build 100% confidence and fulfill your dreams to become an expert service engineer.\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][/vc_tta_tabs][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css_animation="fadeInRight"][vc_column][vc_column_text css_animation="none" el_id="cntid" el_class="cntcls"]\r\n<h3 style="text-align: center;"><strong>AUTOCAD</strong></h3>\r\nAUTOCAD is intended to give an introduction to 2D Computer Aided Drawing. Autodesk’s AutoCAD software is one of the first CAD (Computer-aided design) programs, and is the most widely used CAD application today. AutoCAD is used for 2D and 3D design and drafting in every discipline including; architecture, MEP, civil engineering, mechanical engineering, electrical engineering, structural engineering, electronics, interior design and industrial design. AutoCAD also can be used to generate STL (Stereo Lithography) files for 3D printing. Professionals who use AutoCAD are often referred to as drafters.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css_animation="slideInUp"][vc_column width="1/3"][vc_column_text]\r\n<div class="message-box-wrapper c6wrp red">\r\n<div class="message-box-title">Course Details</div>\r\n<div class="message-box-content">\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><strong>AutoCAD Interface</strong></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Dimensions &amp; Dimension Styles</strong></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Drafting Settings</strong></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Inquiry tools</strong></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Geometry Creation &amp; Modifications</strong></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Block, W-block, X-attach &amp; X-Ref</strong></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Layer &amp; Object properties</strong></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Design centre &amp; Tool Palettes</strong></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Creating &amp; Editing Text</strong></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Template Creation</strong></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>3D parts, UCS, Boolean operation, Solid editing, Model &amp; Paper space</strong></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>View ports &amp; Layouts</strong></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Stretching, Fillets/ Chamfers</strong></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Offsetting</strong></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Arrays, Blocks</strong></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Inserting blocks</strong></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Dynamic blocks</strong></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Design center, Layouts</strong></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Printing, Annotation</strong></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Text, Leaders</strong></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Tables, Hatching</strong></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Dimensions</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/3"][vc_column_text]\r\n<div class="message-box-wrapper c6wrp green">\r\n<div class="message-box-title">Merits</div>\r\n<div class="message-box-content">Explores new career options in the building industry. Increases in the productivity of the designer &amp; helps designer in visualizing the final product that is to be made, it subassemblies and the constituent parts. The product can also be given animation and see how the actual product will work, thus helping the designer to immediately make the modifications if required. CAD helps designer in synthesizing, analyzing, and documenting the design. All these factors help in drastically improving the productivity of the designer that translates into fast designing, lower designing cost and shorter project completion times.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/3"][vc_column_text]\r\n<div class="message-box-wrapper c6wrp blue">\r\n<p class="message-box-title" style="text-align: left;"><strong>Highlights</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<div></div>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li class="message-box-content"><strong>Systematic &amp;Project based training.</strong></li>\r\n 	<li class="message-box-content"><strong>Training conducted in the latest software and exposure given in advanced software’s.</strong></li>\r\n 	<li class="message-box-content"><strong>Advanced implemental of tools including training by working on live projects and case studies and create advanced portfolio.</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column css_animation="slideInLeft" width="1/3"][vc_column_text]\r\n<div class="column-service-wrapper">\r\n\r\n<span class="fa fa-asterisk"> </span>\r\n<div class="column-service-content-wrapper">\r\n<h2 class="column-service-title">COURSE DETAILS</h2>\r\n<div class="column-service-caption">\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><strong>AutoCAD Interface</strong></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Dimensions &amp; Dimension Styles</strong></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Drafting Settings</strong></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Inquiry tools</strong></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Geometry Creation &amp; Modifications</strong></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Block, W-block, X-attach &amp; X-Ref</strong></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Layer &amp; Object properties</strong></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Design centre &amp; Tool Palettes</strong></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Creating &amp; Editing Text</strong></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Template Creation</strong></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>3D parts, UCS, Boolean operation, Solid editing, Model &amp; Paper space</strong></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>View ports &amp; Layouts</strong></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Stretching, Fillets/ Chamfers</strong></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Offsetting</strong></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Arrays, Blocks</strong></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Inserting blocks</strong></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Dynamic blocks</strong></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Design center, Layouts</strong></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Printing, Annotation</strong></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Text, Leaders</strong></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Tables, Hatching</strong></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Dimensions</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column css_animation="slideInUp" width="1/3"][vc_column_text]\r\n<div class="column-service-wrapper">\r\n\r\n<span class="fa fa-trophy"> </span>\r\n<div class="column-service-content-wrapper">\r\n<h2 class="column-service-title">MERITS</h2>\r\n<div class="column-service-caption">Explores new career options in the building industry. Increases in the productivity of the designer &amp; helps designer in visualizing the final product that is to be made, it subassemblies and the constituent parts. The product can also be given animation and see how the actual product will work, thus helping the designer to immediately make the modifications if required. CAD helps designer in synthesizing, analyzing, and documenting the design. All these factors help in drastically improving the productivity of the designer that translates into fast designing, lower designing cost and shorter project completion times.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column css_animation="slideInRight" width="1/3"][vc_column_text]\r\n<div class="column-service-wrapper">\r\n\r\n<span class="fa fa-hand-peace-o"> </span>\r\n<div class="column-service-content-wrapper">\r\n<h2 class="column-service-title">HIGHLIGHTS</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li class="column-service-caption"><strong>Systematic &amp;Project based training.</strong></li>\r\n 	<li class="column-service-caption"><strong>Training conducted in the latest software and exposure given in advanced software’s.</strong></li>\r\n 	<li class="column-service-caption"><strong>Advanced implemental of tools including training by working on live projects and case studies and create advanced portfolio.</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'AUTOCAD', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'autocad', '', '', '2018-04-04 12:23:59', '2018-04-04 12:23:59', '', 0, 'http://localhost/kayaka/?page_id=3649', 0, 'page', '', 0),
