(3652, 1, '2018-03-28 16:07:33', '2018-03-28 16:07:33', '[vc_row el_id="course1id" el_class="corse1cls"][vc_column css=".vc_custom_1522237215804{background-image: url(http://localhost/kayaka/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/ccom.jpg?id=3576) !important;background-position: center !important;background-repeat: no-repeat !important;background-size: cover !important;}" el_id="c1id" el_class="c1cls"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css=".vc_custom_1522253248564{background-color: #ffffff !important;}"][vc_column][vc_tta_tabs active_section="1" css_animation="fadeIn" el_id="contid" el_class="contclass"][vc_tta_section i_position="right" i_icon_fontawesome="fa fa-desktop" add_icon="true" title="Course Info" tab_id="1522240189758-b560af7d-ab63"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3 style="text-align: center;"><strong>COMPUTER COURSE IN OFFICE MANAGEMENT</strong></h3>\r\nComputer plays vital role in every fields. The training on Computer Course is as much as important for an every human being. Assistance of Computer in this technical world is unquestionably to get the task accomplished, especially in the management of office. Generally a person should be aware of using the applications and utilities designed by any developer. The training on Computer Course is as much as important for a every human being. Assistance of Computer in this technical world is unquestionably to get the task accomplished, especially in the management of office.[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section i_position="right" i_icon_fontawesome="fa fa-info-circle" add_icon="true" title="Course Details" tab_id="1522240189931-9ce6ea30-27dc"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3 style="text-align: center;"><strong>COURSE DETAILS</strong></h3>\r\nThe training exposure will be practical with the contents of\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Computer Fundamentals</li>\r\n 	<li>Windows</li>\r\n 	<li>MS Office</li>\r\n 	<li>Internet</li>\r\n 	<li>Typography (English &amp; Kannada)</li>\r\n 	<li>Basic Identification of Hardware &amp; Networking Components</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section i_position="right" i_icon_fontawesome="fa fa-trophy" add_icon="true" title="Merits" tab_id="1522240190131-957dd34e-410f"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h2 style="text-align: center;"><strong>MERITS</strong></h2>\r\nUpon completion of this course a learner will be more confident working individually in any environment. One of the most obvious reasons for a learner to take a computer course is that learning more about using computers improves their chances of getting a better job. If a student sticks with taking computer courses for long enough, he will have a chance to become certified globally to perform certain specialized roles in an organization. Since jobs are more require some computer skills even for entry level positions, taking training in computers is a wise course of action.[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section i_position="right" i_icon_fontawesome="fa fa-hand-peace-o" add_icon="true" title="Highlights" tab_id="1522240190236-268daf5b-3ad7"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3 style="text-align: center;"><strong>HIGHLIGHTS</strong></h3>\r\nThe key findings of the training will be focused more on practicals. Highly experienced and dedicated faculties are available. Individual attention for students. More over 60,000+ learners have successfully completed there by generating the employment in Computer Course in Office Management. Affordable Fees for the students with interactive training methodology.[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][/vc_tta_tabs][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'COMPUTER COURSE IN OFFICE MANAGEMENT', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '3573-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-03-28 16:07:33', '2018-03-28 16:07:33', '', 3573, 'http://localhost/kayaka/index.php/2018/03/28/3573-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
