li>Importing &amp; exporting data from other sources</li>\r\n 	<li>Creating &amp; working with what-if analysis tools</li>\r\n 	<li>Working with Illustration</li>\r\n 	<li>Automation and programmability</li>\r\n 	<li>Workbook management</li>\r\n 	<li>Working with Text, Logical, Date &amp; Time, Financial, Lookup Formula</li>\r\n 	<li>Filtering, sorting, and conditionally formatting data</li>\r\n 	<li>Validating data</li>\r\n 	<li>Using &amp; Customizing Pivot Table &amp; Pivot Chart</li>\r\n 	<li>Excel and the Web</li>\r\n 	<li>Working in a different language</li>\r\n 	<li>Collaboration of Excel Sheet</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section i_position="right" i_icon_fontawesome="fa fa-trophy" add_icon="true" title="Merits" tab_id="1522240190131-957dd34e-410f"][vc_column_text css_animation="none"]\r\n<h3 style="text-align: center;"><strong>MERITS</strong></h3>\r\nMaster Shortcuts, functions and formulas that save time and increases productivity. Reduces workload at every interval of time by automating repetitive tasks by using macros. Learning how to use Advance Excel to its maximum potential will add a weight age, improves your skills and will open up more opportunities for employment.\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section i_position="right" i_icon_fontawesome="fa fa-hand-peace-o" add_icon="true" title="Highlights" tab_id="1522240190236-268daf5b-3ad7"][vc_column_text css_animation="none"]\r\n<h3 style="text-align: center;"><strong>HIGHLIGHTS</strong></h3>\r\nThe most important highlight is we have primed the deliverable with different scenario of an organization. The book will equip you with excellent Excel skills, good enough to learn quickly. Instruction is logically structured into sessions and lessons.\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][/vc_tta_tabs][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text css_animation="none"]\r\n<h3 style="text-align: center;"><strong>DATA MANAGEMENT AND ANALYSIS USING ADVANCED EXCEL\