(3673, 1, '2018-03-29 07:36:50', '2018-03-29 07:36:50', '[vc_row el_id="course4id" el_class="corse4cls"][vc_column css_animation="fadeInLeft" css=".vc_custom_1522308129765{background-image: url(http://localhost/kayaka/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/New-Project-3-1.jpg?id=3672) !important;background-position: center !important;background-repeat: no-repeat !important;background-size: cover !important;}" el_id="c1id" el_class="c1cls"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css=".vc_custom_1522308380893{background-color: #f4f4f4 !important;}" el_id="hdid" el_class="hdcls"][vc_column][vc_tta_tabs active_section="1" css_animation="fadeIn" el_id="contid" el_class="contclass"][vc_tta_section i_position="right" i_icon_fontawesome="fa fa-desktop" add_icon="true" title="Course Info" tab_id="1522240189758-b560af7d-ab63"][vc_column_text css_animation="none"]\r\n<h3 style="text-align: center;"><strong>SOFTWARE TRAINING\r\n</strong></h3>\r\nSoftware training provides a fully pledged detail where a participant can develop his technical skills and become a software developer. The training on software training is as much as important for an every jobseeker.\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section i_position="right" i_icon_fontawesome="fa fa-info-circle" add_icon="true" title="Course Details" tab_id="1522240189931-9ce6ea30-27dc"][vc_column_text css_animation="none"]\r\n<h3 style="text-align: center;"><strong>COURSE DETAILS</strong></h3>\r\nThe training exposure will be practical with the contents of\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>C</li>\r\n 	<li>C++</li>\r\n 	<li>Java</li>\r\n 	<li>Advanced Java</li>\r\n 	<li>Unix</li>\r\n 	<li>.Net</li>\r\n 	<li>Multimedia Animation</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section i_position="right" i_icon_fontawesome="fa fa-trophy" add_icon="true" title="Merits" tab_id="1522240190131-957dd34e-410f"][vc_column_text css_animation="none"]\r\n<h3 style="text-align: center;"><strong>MERITS</strong></h3>\r\nThis course will enable the learner to improve the importance, objectives and principles of software training. The course concentrates on the object paradigm including classes, inheritance, virtual functions, and templates in the development of Programs. [/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section i_position="right" i_icon_fontawesome="fa fa-hand-peace-o" add_icon="true" title="Highlights" tab_id="1522240190236-268daf5b-3ad7"][vc_column_text css_animation="none"]\r\n<h3 style="text-align: center;"><strong>HIGHLIGHTS</strong></h3>\r\nWe are providing the essential training for Software development courses. These courses will teach how to prepare the software and how to implement and analysis the software and these courses useful for develop software’s like Java Apps, java mobiles, programs. and C,C++,Java programmers can work in any fields and for this purpose mainly we will teach the programs with daily life examples and more practical with every topics.\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][/vc_tta_tabs][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text css_animation="none"]\r\n<h3 style="text-align: center;"><strong>SOFTWARE TRAINING\r\n</strong></h3>\r\nSoftware training provides a fully pledged detail where a participant can develop his technical skills and become a software developer. The training on software training is as much as important for an every jobseeker.\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width="1/3"][vc_column_text]\r\n<div class="message-box-wrapper c3wrp red">\r\n<div class="message-box-title">Course Details</div>\r\n<div class="message-box-content">\r\n\r\nThe training exposure will be practical with the contents of\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><strong>C</strong></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>C++</strong></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Java</strong></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Advanced Java</strong></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Unix</strong></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>.Net</strong></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Multimedia Animation</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/3"][vc_column_text]\r\n<div class="message-box-wrapper c3wrp green">\r\n<div class="message-box-title">Merits</div>\r\n<div class="message-box-content">This course will enable the learner to improve the importance, objectives and principles of software training. The course concentrates on the object paradigm including classes, inheritance, virtual functions, and templates in the development of Programs.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/3"][vc_column_text]\r\n<div class="message-box-wrapper c3wrp blue">\r\n<p class="message-box-title" style="text-align: left;"><strong>Highlights</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div class="message-box-content">We are providing the essential training for Software development courses. These courses will teach how to prepare the software and how to implement and analysis the software and these courses useful for develop software’s like Java Apps, java mobiles, programs. and C,C++,Java programmers can work in any fields and for this purpose mainly we will teach the programs with daily life examples and more practical with every topics.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width="1/3"][vc_column_text]\r\n<div class="column-service-wrapper">\r\n\r\n<span class="fa fa-asterisk"> </span>\r\n<div class="column-service-content-wrapper">\r\n<h2 class="column-service-title">COURSE DETAILS</h2>\r\n<div class="column-service-caption">\r\n\r\nTo enhance learners, we provide\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Basic English <b>(Listening, Reading, Writing, Pronunciation, Word Building, Vocabulary).</b></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Structural English <b>(Parts of Speech, Tenses, Direct &amp; Indirect Speech, Letter Writing, Paragraph Writing).</b></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Communicative English <b>(Seeking Permission, Asking for Advice, Environmental Conversation, Drafting Bio-Data, Resume).</b></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/3"][vc_column_text]\r\n<div class="column-service-wrapper">\r\n\r\n<span class="fa fa-trophy"> </span>\r\n<div class="column-service-content-wrapper">\r\n<h2 class="column-service-title">MERITS</h2>\r\n<div class="column-service-caption">Now days, to become proficiency. English is very essential. This course also helps to empower their Business language. On completion of this course students are enable to enrich their vocabulary, pronunciation, word building, enhance their knowledge in usage of grammar by understanding Parts of speech, Articles and Tenses etc., and also communicative skill to master both Verbal and Non-Verbal communication. They will be able to get experience of speaking real English by involving in various group discussions, pick-and-speak, mock interviews, etc.,</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/3"][vc_column_text]\r\n<div class="column-service-wrapper">\r\n\r\n<span class="fa fa-hand-peace-o"> </span>\r\n<div class="column-service-content-wrapper">\r\n<h2 class="column-service-title">HIGHLIGHTS</h2>\r\n<div class="column-service-caption">We provide many advanced courses in our institution where Spoken English is also one among the leading course. We provide Spoken English course to promote employment opportunities. We groom their confidence, personality by training on various skills such as Interview skill, Communicative skill and also interpersonal skill. On successful completion of the course, students are capable of speaking fluent English. We have trained thousands of candidates from various categories.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'SOFTWARE TRAINING', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '3604-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-03-29 07:36:50', '2018-03-29 07:36:50', '', 3604, 'http://localhost/kayaka/index.php/2018/03/29/3604-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
