(3806, 1, '2018-04-04 14:01:12', '2018-04-04 14:01:12', '[vc_row][vc_column css_animation="none"][vc_column_text]\r\n<div class="applybs">\r\n<div id="countid" class="row countrow animatedParent">\r\n<div class="col-lg-2 col-md-2 col-sm-6 col-xs-12">\r\n<div class="icon"><span class="fa fa-building"> </span></div>\r\n<div class="stats"><span class="number" data-id="1999">1999</span>\r\nEstablished in 1999 as Kayaka Balaga and incorporated as Kayaka Computer Education (P) ltd in 2004.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="col-lg-2 col-md-2 col-sm-6 col-xs-12 cnts">\r\n<div class="icon"><span class="fa fa-briefcase"> </span></div>\r\n<div class="stats"><span class="number" data-id="45">45</span><span class="pls">+</span>\r\nMoreover 45+ centers in karnataka and still growing.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="col-lg-2 col-md-2 col-sm-6 col-xs-12 cnts">\r\n<div class="icon"><span class="fa fa-certificate"> </span></div>\r\n<div class="stats"><span class="number" data-id="20">20</span><span class="pls">+</span>\r\n20+ Certification and Skill Oriented courses.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="col-lg-2 col-md-2 col-sm-6 col-xs-12 cnts">\r\n<div class="icon"><span class="fa fa-user"> </span></div>\r\n<div class="stats"><span class="number" data-id="300000">300000</span><span class="pls">+</span>\r\nMoreover 300000+ satisfied learners since 2004.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="col-lg-2 col-md-2 col-sm-6 col-xs-12 cnts">\r\n<div class="icon"><span class="fa fa-map-marker"> </span></div>\r\n<div class="stats"><span class="number" data-id="3">3</span><span class="pls">+</span>\r\nRecognised from state and national Skill Sector bodies.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'main', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '9-autosave-v1', '', '', '2018-04-04 14:01:12', '2018-04-04 14:01:12', '', 9, 'http://localhost/kayaka/9-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(3807, 1, '2018-04-04 10:58:00', '2018-04-04 10:58:00', '[vc_row el_id="abtid" el_class="abtcls"][vc_column css_animation="none" width="1/2" css=".vc_custom_1522072227874{background-image: url(http://localhost/kayaka/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/slide1.jpg?id=3460) !important;background-position: center !important;background-repeat: no-repeat !important;background-size: cover !important;}" el_id="imgid1" el_class="imgcls1"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2" el_id="kayid" el_class="kaycls"][vc_column_text css_animation="none" el_class="abcls" el_id="abid"]KAYAKA was established in the year 1999 which has successfully undergone training for more over 3 lacs learners from all sectors till date. Later in 2007 it has been incorporated as KAYAKA COMPUTER EDUCATION (P) LTD. Kayaka, not only limits its services in the urban areas but also provides more effective service in and around Karnataka in the field of Computerized Accounts through Tally.ERP 9, Software, Hardware and Networking, CAD, Mobile Technology, Spoken English, Data Management and Analysis using Advanced Excel, Soft Skills Training &amp; Banking Coaching classes to fulfil the learners with Computer literacy to avail better employment. [/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row el_id="rid1" el_class="rcls1"][vc_column width="1/2" el_id="kayid2" el_class="kaycls2"][vc_column_text css_animation="none" el_id="abtid2" el_class="abtcls2"]Our innovative training methodology is a result of years of research by educationalists and human resource professionals. We welcome Students, Employees, Individuals, Businessmen and people from all walks of life to groom their career for success. Our training course inspires and encourages them to reach for their goals. The various courses which are offered through Certificate courses are constantly updated according to the current trend in the IT industry. Training is conducted in comfortable and spacious labs equipped with computers which are constantly updated with the latest technology.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column css_animation="none" width="1/2" css=".vc_custom_1522071922160{background-image: url(http://localhost/kayaka/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/corporate_training9-1-639x359.jpg?id=3541) !important;background-position: center !important;background-repeat: no-repeat !important;background-size: cover !important;}" el_id="imgid2" el_class="imgcls2"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row el_id="rid2" el_class="rc2"][vc_column css_animation="none" width="1/2" css=".vc_custom_1522071885959{background-image: url(http://localhost/kayaka/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/3-1.jpg?id=3546) !important;background-position: center !important;background-repeat: no-repeat !important;background-size: cover !important;}" el_id="imgid3" el_class="imgcls3"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2" el_id="kayid3" el_class="kaycls3"][vc_column_text css_animation="none" el_id="abtid3" el_class="abtcls3"]We are Tally Authorized training provider known as Tally Institute of Learning TIL and also Master Tally Assessment partner in Karnataka region. Certification in Tally.ERP9 gives a competitive edge with Tally software training certifications from Tally Academy. Globally recognized, Tally certifications demonstrate that you have honed your skills through rigorous study and direct experience in your area of expertise. The key features of our TIL are scientifically designed teaching methodology, industry relevant curriculum/ courseware, training delivery by Tally certified faculty, with effective theory to practical sessions, online assessments, verifiable certification and 100% placement assistance.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row el_id="rid3" el_class="rcl3"][vc_column width="1/2" el_id="kayid4" el_class="kaycls4"][vc_column_text el_id="abtid4" el_class="abtcls4"]Tally powers more than 90% of business houses in India. This propels demand for Tally trained professionals. With Tally being used in more than 100 countries, students gain access to global placement 