(3833, 1, '2018-04-04 12:27:43', '2018-04-04 12:27:43', '[vc_row el_id="course4id" el_class="corse4cls"][vc_column css_animation="fadeInLeft" css=".vc_custom_1522327387192{background-image: url(http://localhost/kayaka/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/banner-2.jpg?id=3701) !important;background-position: center !important;background-repeat: no-repeat !important;background-size: cover !important;}" el_id="c1id" el_class="c1cls"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css=".vc_custom_1522257137413{background-color: #ffffff !important;}" el_id="hdid" el_class="hdcls"][vc_column][vc_tta_tabs active_section="1" css_animation="fadeIn" el_id="contid" el_class="contclass"][vc_tta_section i_position="right" i_icon_fontawesome="fa fa-desktop" add_icon="true" title="Course Info" tab_id="1522240189758-b560af7d-ab63"][vc_column_text css_animation="none"]\r\n<h3 style="text-align: center;"><strong>CHIP LEVEL SERVICING\r\n</strong></h3>\r\nChip Level Servicing from basic to BGA level by servicing them in today’s computer world. This course also enables the learner to become a own entrepreneur.\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section i_position="right" i_icon_fontawesome="fa fa-info-circle" add_icon="true" title="Course Details" tab_id="1522240189931-9ce6ea30-27dc"][vc_column_text css_animation="none"]\r\n<h3 style="text-align: center;"><strong>COURSE DETAILS</strong></h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><strong>Motherboard</strong></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>SMD Components</strong></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Motherboard Working</strong></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Motherboard(Various Sections, SMPS, Power Section)</strong></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Motherboard Cold Checking</strong></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Processor Section</strong></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Chipset Section</strong></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Memory Section</strong></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Front &amp; Rear Panel Section</strong></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Components Soldering &amp; Disordering</strong></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>BIOS Section</strong></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>CMOS Section</strong></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>VGA Section</strong></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Troubleshooting</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section i_position="right" i_icon_fontawesome="fa fa-trophy" add_icon="true" title="Merits" tab_id="1522240190131-957dd34e-410f"][vc_column_text css_animation="none"]\r\n<h3 style="text-align: center;"><strong>MERITS</strong></h3>\r\nThe teaching staffs have a background of electronics graduation with more than 10 years of chip level repairs experience backup. So here students not only understand the basic electronics, basic working phenomena of motherboards which is an essential for this profession to learn the real practical experience of repair.\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section i_position="right" i_icon_fontawesome="fa fa-hand-peace-o" add_icon="true" title="Highlights" tab_id="1522240190236-268daf5b-3ad7"][vc_column_text css_animation="none"]\r\n<h3 style="text-align: center;"><strong>HIGHLIGHTS</strong></h3>\r\nWe also have an infrastructure in such a way that each student will have their own individual testing equipments and tools to concentrate and learn in proper way during course period. We organized ourselves in such a way that we concentrate on each student by understanding his/her capability and teach according to it. So this course is not only suitable to the fresh students but also to the people who are already in the field and struggling to understand the systematic concept of repair. We assure that we build 100% confidence and fulfill your dreams to become an expert service engineer.\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][/vc_tta_tabs][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css_animation="bounceInRight"][vc_column][vc_column_text css_animation="none" el_id="cntid" el_class="cntcls"]\r\n<h3 style="text-align: center;"><strong>GRAPHIC DESIGNER</strong></h3>\r\nDomain – The Graphic Designing: Graphic Designing is a perennial industry. Everlasting business. Development in any business required Pamphlets – Posters – Brochures – Hoardings – Books – Book Covers – Calendars – and many print materials. Customer: Every person is a customer who uses even business cards. Profession: The best career for the creative people, skilled people. Career: Anyone can make your life time career in this domain which starts as a D T P Operator can end up with high-paid Art Director in their career\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css_animation="bounceInUp"][vc_column width="1/3"][vc_column_text]\r\n<div class="message-box-wrapper c8wrp red">\r\n<div class="message-box-title">Course Details</div>\r\n<div class="message-box-content">The training exposure will be practical with the contents of</div>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><strong>Windows</strong></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>HTML</strong></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Java Script</strong></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Cascade Style Sheets</strong></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Dream Weaver</strong></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Adobe Photoshop</strong></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Adobe Flash</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/3"][vc_column_text]\r\n<div class="message-box-wrapper c8wrp green">\r\n<div class="message-box-title">Merits</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li class="message-box-content"><strong>Can handle work from any place.</strong></li>\r\n 	<li class="message-box-content"><strong>By developing website can become an Entrepreneur.</strong></li>\r\n 	<li class="message-box-content"><strong>Add-on value to your knowledge to widen up your career &amp; opportunities in the field of web designing.</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/3"][vc_column_text]\r\n<div class="message-box-wrapper c8wrp blue">\r\n<p class="message-box-title" style="text-align: left;"><strong>Highlights</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><strong>Teaching the key principles of web design.</strong></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Train in art of building effective and attractive websit